<file path="README.md">
# 🎓 LearnMate: A Gamified Learning Platform

**LearnMate** is a full-stack, gamified learning platform designed to make education engaging and collaborative. With features like real-time chat, interactive quizzes, a to-do task system, and an AI-powered doubt assistant, LearnMate aims to revolutionize how students learn and connect online.
![Preview](./assets/preview.png)


## 🚀 Features

- 🔐 **Secure Authentication**  
  Role-based access for students and admins with encrypted login/logout system.

- 🎮 **Gamified Task Management**  
  - Personalized to-do lists  
  - Progress tracking  
  - Reward points 
  - Dynamic leaderboard

- ❓ **AI Doubt Assistant (Gemini API)**  
  Instant doubt resolution powered by Google’s Gemini API.

- 🧠 **Interactive Quizzes & Games**  
  - Multiple-choice quizzes  
  - Educational mini-games  
  - Real-time score calculation

- 💬 **Real-Time Chat**  
  Connect with classmates and study together

- 📚 **Resource Sharing Portal**  
  Share notes, links, and study materials with peers.

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Layer        | Technology                  |
|--------------|-----------------------------|
| Backend      | Node.js, Express.js         |
| Frontend     | React.js, EJS, Tailwind CSS |
| Database     | MongoDB                     |
| AI Assistant | Gemini API                  |
</file>

